title: Just for Laughs-Damn Yankees Hosted by Lewis Black (2006) [PDTV]
description:
Just For Laughs: Damn Yankees Hosted by: Lewis Black
Aired: 2006

Canada and the U.S. finally unite when Just For Laughs Damn Yankees brings you a night of hilarity that closely examine the Seven Deadly Sins of our neighbours to the South. There's more and more Greed, a fill of Gluttony, wish for some Envy, be glad about Pride, gaze longingly at some Lust, get mad enough to watch Wrath, and... some Sloth... if you can get around to it. Featuring some of the best talent to ever take the stage at the world's largest comedy festival, including Canadian stars: Rick Mercer, Brent Butt and Jeremy Hotz and U.S. comics Joan Rivers, Jon Stewart, Greg Giraldo, Tim Allen, Bill Maher and more.
